Package com.sun.identity.authentication.spi

Interface DSAMECallbackInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Callback
    public interface DSAMECallbackInterface
extends Callback
    The DSAMECallbackInterface interface needs to be implemented by services and applications which want to define custom Callbacks. Look at javax.security.auth.callback javadocs for details on Callbacks.
